<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="External_links">External links</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Rabbinic_authority&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: External links"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.sefaria.org/Rabbinic_Authority_I">A. Y. Warburg, <i>Rabbinic Authority: The Vision and the Reality</i>, Urim Publications. Jerusalem, 2013.</a> (full text available online).</li></ul>
